This paper deals with caching in cellular networks, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of networked systems and communication in computer science. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper involves optimization of caching policies, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also mentions coordinated multipoint transmission techniques, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
